title: Forum at Mizzou: The late Bob Brookmeyer On Composing And Soloing
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - This clip is from a forum at the University of Missouri with Bob Brookmeyer and Dan Morgenstern. Bob discusses the relationship between composing and soloing.
